      "id": "PopularPost353429",
      "post_content": "Let\u2019s say your opponent casts a spell you want to counter. Respond by activating this, then respond to your own activation by casting [Memory Lapse](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Memory Lapse). The spell will be countered, then go to the top of your opponent\u2019s library, where it will then get milled into his/her graveyard!  \n  \nOh wait a minute. Any ordinary counter sends cards to the graveyard anyway! Whoops. Ignore\u2026",
